      amount but no currence, i.e. Money(123, None).
    - MoneyField supports default of type bytes
  - Added
    - Add support for Django 4.0 and 4.1.
    - Add support for Python 3.10.
  - Removed
    - Drop support for Django 3.1.
    - Drop support for Python 3.6.
